Setup:
Register at cds: https://cds.climate.copernicus.eu/user/register?destination=%2F%23!%2Fhome
Login
Navigate to https://cds.climate.copernicus.eu/api-how-to
Copy the code to ~/.cdsapirc
Accept the Licence to use Copernicus Products' at https://cds.climate.copernicus.eu/cdsapp/#!/terms/licence-to-use-copernicus-products
install requirements
chmod +x ./bin/get_data.sh
chmod +x ./bin/add_pressure_gph.sh

Data retrieval:
Use command
./bin/get_data.sh <date> <time>
E.g. for the second of march 2020 at 12 o'clock, execute
./bin/get_data.sh 2020-03-02 12:00:00
